{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "After creating these models, participants reflected on ethical implications related to the trustworthiness of generative models, copyright issues, and environmental impact.",
    "They also reflected on the importance of data quality and quantity in the training dataset and voiced a more refined understanding of the functionality of generative language models.",
    "Our study demonstrates the feasibility of engaging young people in the design of GLMs.",
    "Compared to other studies in which youth learned about the functionality of generative models and explored their outputs as users (Solyst et al., 2024) engaging youth in construction activities made more transparent the process of building models.",
    "Building babyGPTs supported youth to question the \"aesthetic legitimacy\" of outputs (Solyst et al., 2024) and develop nuanced understandings of the functionality and ethics of GLMs."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
